(
<figureCitation id="83AB39AFCE2802136C3BFC67679D33FE" box="[367,445,984,1008]" captionStart="FIGURAS 13‑18" captionStartId="12.[132,222,1826,1845]" captionTargetBox="[169,1213,170,1779]" captionTargetId="figure-1@12.[132,1266,170,1792]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURAS 13‑18: 13. Agrilus timorosus sp.nov.(holótipo). 14. Agrilus vanini sp.nov.(holótipo). 15. Agrilus yeti sp. nov. (holótipo).16. Agrilus aegrotus sp. nov. (edeago, 1 mm). 17. Agrilus casarii sp. nov. (edeago, holótipo, 1,9 mm). 18. Agrilus crux sp. nov. (edeago, 1,3 mm)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4656312" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/4656312/files/figure.png" pageId="18" pageNumber="99">Fig. 14</figureCitation>
